# nfat_arch

**Instance Property**

An integer specifying the number of [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/kernel/fat_arch] data structures that follow. This is the number of architectures contained in this binary.

## Declaration

```swift
uint32_t nfat_arch;
```
